Metavariable P:Statement
Metavariable Q:Statement

Rule (BiconditionalIntroduction)
  Premises    
    P ⇒ Q
    Q ⇒ P
  Conclusion
    P 𝗂𝖿𝖿 Q

Rule (BiconditionalLeftElimination)
  Premise
    P 𝗂𝖿𝖿 Q
  Conclusion
    P ⇒ Q

Rule (BiconditionalRightElimination)
  Premise
    P 𝗂𝖿𝖿 Q
  Conclusion
    Q ⇒ P
